com.snap2d.world

Class EntityManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.snap2d.world.EntityManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Renderable

    public class EntityManager
extends Object
implements Renderable
    Provides a facility for managing registered Entity objects. Adding EntityManager as a Renderable task will allow all render/update calls to be forwarded to Entities registered with EntityManager. EntityManager also checks for collisions between all registered Entities on each update and fires a CollisionEvent when Entity collisions are detected. EntityListeners can also be used to receive events for when a new Entity is registered or removed.

    Note: EntityManager is NOT thread safe. Only one thread should be responsible for modifying its data, or the Object must be synchronized externally.
    Author:
    Brian Groenke
